tr: the quality of having great facility and competence
skillfulness in the command of fundamentals deriving from practice and familiarity

value.def: If you show proficiency in something, you show ability or skill at it.

example.ex: Evidence of basic proficiency in English is part of the admission requirement.
example.tran: 英语基本熟练是入学条件之一。

trans: 英语水平；英语能力；英文程度；英语熟练；英文能力
能力验证试验；能力验证；实验室能力验证；能力比对检验；熟练度测试
